commit.message:
noad-0.8.8: new version - maintenance release

change version number in files, update ChangeLog
configure.ac: change code to work with /bin/sh -> /bin/dash
remove mkinstalldirs (from old build system)
.gitignore: add more files
autogen.sh: add full version

replace COPYING with current version

reported in https://github.com/madmartin/noad/issues/1
thanks for reporting.

noad-0.8.7: new version - maintenance release

change version number in files, update ChangeLog

fix compile problems with musl-libc

necessary changes to allow compile with musl-libc:
- include limits.h, necessary for musl-libc, redundant for glibc
- conditionally define DEFFILEMODE
- execinfo.h does not exist, include only with glibc
- this results in the absence of functions for printing a stacktrace
- conditionally make function show_stackframe() a NOOP
- conditionally exclude print_stacktrace()
remove unused code to reduce compile warnings
fix clang-12 compile warning
fix clang-11 compile error
fix gcc-11 compile errors
remove compiler warnings of type -Wtrigraphs
remove compiler warnings of type -Wformat=
channels.h: fix file mode of channels.h
add autogen.sh for easy use of autoconf/automake

configure.ac: let "ar" be detected via AM_PROG_AR

add C_USE_SYSTEM_EXTENSIONS statement to silence warnings
remove automake/autoconf generated files from repo

.gitignore: add output of the autoconf/automake commands

the files produced by autoconf/automake should not appear in the repository
update README files

convert text files to UTF-8

Signed-off-by: Martin Dummer <martin.dummer@gmx.net>

change version string, add changes to readme
